    {"id": "p6", "text": "Bukayo Saka is Arsenal's key player on the right wing. The young Englishman is known for his directness, creativity, and ability to score and assist. He has been Arsenal's most important player under Mikel Arteta and is a key figure for England."},
    {"id": "p7", "text": "Phil Foden is Manchester City's homegrown talent who has developed into one of England's best players. He can play as a winger, attacking midfielder, or false nine. He is known for his technical ability, vision, and intelligent movement."},
    {"id": "p8", "text": "Rodri is Manchester City's defensive midfielder and won the Ballon d'Or in 2024. The Spanish international is known for his positioning, passing, and ability to control the tempo of games. He is the engine of Guardiola's system."},
    {"id": "p9", "text": "Martin Odegaard is Arsenal's captain and creative hub. The Norwegian attacking midfielder is known for his technical ability, pressing work rate, and ability to find pockets of space. He has been crucial to Arsenal's title challenges."},
    {"id": "p10", "text": "Alisson Becker is Liverpool's Brazilian goalkeeper, considered one of the best in the world. Known for his shot-stopping, distribution, and composure. His arrival at Liverpool alongside Van Dijk transformed them into Premier League and Champions League winners."},
    {"id": "p11", "text": "Jude Bellingham became one of the most complete young midfielders in world football after moving from Borussia Dortmund to Real Madrid. He is known for ball carrying, pressing, leadership, late runs into the box, and scoring important goals."},
    {"id": "p12", "text": "Kylian Mbappe is one of the fastest and most dangerous forwards in football. He is known for explosive acceleration, direct dribbling, elite finishing, and his ability to attack space behind defenses."},
    {"id": "p13", "text": "Lionel Messi is widely regarded as one of the greatest footballers of all time. He is known for dribbling, vision, passing, free kicks, finishing, and his long career of success with Barcelona, Argentina, and Inter Miami."},
    {"id": "p14", "text": "Cristiano Ronaldo is one of football's greatest goalscorers. He is known for athleticism, heading, finishing, movement, mentality, and success with Manchester United, Real Madrid, Juventus, Portugal, and Al Nassr."},
    {"id": "p15", "text": "Neymar is a Brazilian forward known for flair, dribbling, creativity, close control, and one-versus-one ability. He starred for Santos, Barcelona, Paris Saint-Germain, Brazil, and later Al Hilal."},
    {"id": "p16", "text": "Luka Modric is a Croatian midfielder known for technical elegance, press resistance, passing, and game intelligence. He has been central to Real Madrid's Champions League success and won the Ballon d'Or in 2018."},
    {"id": "p17", "text": "Toni Kroos was a German midfielder known for passing accuracy, tempo control, set pieces, and composure under pressure. He played a major role in Real Madrid and Germany's success."},
    {"id": "p18", "text": "Sergio Ramos is a Spanish defender known for leadership, aggressive defending, aerial ability, and scoring important goals. He was a key figure for Real Madrid and Spain."},
    {"id": "p19", "text": "Karim Benzema is a French striker known for link-up play, movement, finishing, and intelligence. He became Real Madrid's main attacking leader after Cristiano Ronaldo left and won the Ballon d'Or in 2022."},
    {"id": "p20", "text": "Robert Lewandowski is one of the best strikers of his generation. He is known for clinical finishing, positioning, heading, and consistency, especially during his time at Borussia Dortmund, Bayern Munich, and Barcelona."},
    {"id": "p21", "text": "Vinicius Junior is a Brazilian winger for Real Madrid known for speed, dribbling, directness, and improved finishing. He is especially dangerous in transition and one-on-one situations."},
    {"id": "p22", "text": "Pedri is a Spanish midfielder for Barcelona known for intelligence, close control, passing, and calmness under pressure. He is often compared to classic Barcelona midfielders because of his technical style."},
    {"id": "p23", "text": "Gavi is a Spanish midfielder for Barcelona known for intensity, pressing, aggression, and technical quality. Despite his young age, he plays with high energy and maturity."},
    {"id": "p24", "text": "Declan Rice is an English midfielder known for ball-winning, defensive positioning, carrying the ball forward, and leadership. He became a key player for Arsenal after joining from West Ham."},
    {"id": "p25", "text": "Bruno Fernandes is Manchester United's creative midfielder known for chance creation, risk-taking passes, pressing, penalties, and long-range shooting."},
    {"id": "p26", "text": "Marcus Rashford is a Manchester United forward known for pace, direct running, shooting power, and attacking transitions. He is most dangerous when driving into space from the left."},
    {"id": "p27", "text": "Son Heung-min is a Tottenham Hotspur forward known for two-footed finishing, speed, movement, and counter-attacking threat. He has been one of the Premier League's most consistent attackers."},
    {"id": "p28", "text": "Cole Palmer developed into one of Chelsea's most important attacking players after leaving Manchester City. He is known for composure, creativity, penalties, dribbling, and decision-making in the final third."},
