    {"id": "m4", "text": "Carlo Ancelotti is known for calm leadership, tactical adaptability, man-management, and success in the Champions League. He has managed elite clubs including AC Milan, Chelsea, PSG, Bayern Munich, Everton, and Real Madrid."},
